verbose_text: Our ex vivo experiments revealed that Hs2st -/- CSB has difficulty maintaining a stable [Fgf8] gradient and increased Erk sensitivity to Fgf8, while Hs6st1 -/- CSB has significantly increased Fgf8 levels compared to WT and decreased Erk sensitivity to Fgf8.
evidence: Hs2st -/-  CSB has difficulty maintaining a stable [Fgf8] gradient and increased Erk sensitivity to Fgf8
